>> title: Bruto Negroni
>> tags: gin,tumbler,rolled,three-ingredient

Add @ice{1%large cube} to #tumbler{}.

Combine @Carpano Antica sweet vermouth{3/4%oz} and @Bruto Americano{3/4%oz} in tumbler.

Add @gin{1.5%oz} to tumbler.

Roll ingredients together in glass or lightly stir with finger.

Garnish optionally with @orange peel{1} after express orange oil on glass.